{"serial": "11085", "department_serial": 10, "code": "CL3053", "class": "*", "name": {"en": "Introduction to Buddhism", "ch": "佛學概論"}, "notice": {"en": "", "ch": ""}, "instructor": {"en": ["HSU, MING-CHIEN"], "ch": ["徐銘謙"]}, "credits": 2, "time_loc": [{"time": {"week": 3, "session": ["7", "8"]}, "loc": {"building": "C2", "room": "110"}}], "isRequired": false, "isFullSem": true, "MaxStu": 50, "department": {"ch": "中國文學系", "en": "Department of Chinese Literature"}, "system": {"ch": "學士班", "en": "Undergraduate Programme"}, "language": {"ch": "國語", "en": "Chinese"}, "card": {"ch": "不使用", "en": "None"}, "assigned": 1, "selected": 45, "remark": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "goal": {"ch": "佛教自印度肇興，至漢代輸入中國伊始，典籍浩瀚，教理綿密，百家爭鳴，宗派林立。如今佛學研究業已深入文學、哲學、語言學……等各領域。本課程作為佛教學術研究入門，以歷史發展為線索，細究史牒，商量教義，帶領學生認識印度佛教的起源與中國佛教的分立，並能熟悉佛學基本課題。期許論列陳跡之餘，達濟宏觀認識之目的。", "en": "After Indian Buddhism was introduced to China in the Han Dynasty, it developed in a diverse way. Nowadays, Buddhist studies have penetrated into various fields such as literature, philosophy, linguistics, etc. This course is an introduction to Buddhism, it will lead students to understand the development of Buddhism in India and China, and then becoming familiar with basic topics in Buddhism. It is expected that students will have a macro understanding of Buddhism."}, "outline": {"ch": "第01週：課程說明（含學期講義、參考書目、常用工具資料庫）\n第02週：佛教的學術課題\n第03週：悉達多與佛教的起源\n第04週：經律論與教團的分立\n第05週：大乘思想與中國佛教的肇始\n第06週：佛學基本觀念──四諦\n第07週：佛學基本觀念──三法印與緣起\n第08週：中觀學派概述\n第09週：期中分組口頭報告\n第10週：唯識學派概述\n第11週：如來藏與大乘起信論\n第12週：天台宗概述（一）\n第13週：天台宗概述（二）\n第14週：華嚴宗概述（一）\n第15週：華嚴宗概述（二）\n第16週：菩提達摩與禪宗\n第17週：期末筆試\n第18週：指定閱讀討論──南宗禪的發展", "en": "Week 01: Course description (including semester handouts, bibliography, and common tools database)\nWeek 02: Academic Topics in Buddhism\nWeek 03: Siddhārtha and the Origins of Buddhism\nWeek 04: Tripiṭaka and sajgha\nWeek 05: Mahayana Thought and the Beginning of Chinese Buddhism\nWeek 06: Basic Concepts of Buddhism──Four Noble Truths\nWeek 07: Basic Concepts of Buddhism──Three Dharma Seals and Pratītyasamutpāda\nWeek 08: Overview of the Madhyamaka School\nWeek 09: Midterm group report\nWeek 10: Overview of the Yogachara\nWeek 11: Tathagatagarbha and Awakening of Faith in the Mahayana\nWeek 12: Overview of Tiantai Sect (1)\nWeek 13: Overview of Tiantai Sect (2)\nWeek 14: Overview of Huayan Sect (1)\nWeek 15: Overview of Huayan Sect (2)\nWeek 16: Bodhidharma and Zen\nWeek 17: Final Exam\nWeek 18: Assigned Reading──The Development of Southern Zen"}, "textbook": {"ch": "教科書：自編講義\n參考書：林朝成、郭朝順，《佛學概論》（臺北：三民，2023）。吳汝鈞，《印度佛學的現代詮釋》（臺北：文津，1995）。吳汝鈞，《中國佛學的現代詮釋》（臺北：文津，1998）。楊惠南，《佛教思想發展史論》（臺北：東大，2003）。蔣維喬，《寫給年輕人的佛學入門》（臺北：商周，2017）。關大眠著，鄭柏銘譯，《佛學概論》（南京：譯林，2013）。", "en": "Textbook: Self-compiled handouts\nReference book: Lin Chaocheng and Guo Chaoshun. Introduction to Buddhism. Taipei: Sanmin Press, 2023. Wu Rujun. Modern Interpretation of Indian Buddhism. Taipei: Wenjin Press, 1995. Wu Rujun. Modern Interpretation of Chinese Buddhism. Taipei: Wenjin Press, 1998. Yang Huinan. History of the Development of Buddhist Thought. Taipei: Dongda University Press, 2003. Jiang Weiqiao. Introduction to Buddhism for Young People. Taipei: Shangzhou Press, 2017. Keown, Damien. Introduction to Buddhism. Nanjing: Yilin Press, 2013."}, "selfCompiledRate": {"ch": "30", "en": "30"}, "instructMethod": {"ch": "講授\n研討", "en": ["Lecture", "Seminar"]}, "gradMethod": {"ch": "平時（含課堂討論與出席）40％，期中分組口頭報告30％，期末筆試30％。", "en": "Regular grades (including class discussions and attendance) are 40％, mid-term group reports are 30％, and final exams are 30％."}, "officeHour": {"ch": "無", "en": "none"}, "teachWeeks": {"ch": "17+1", "en": "17+1"}, "flexDiscription": {"ch": "開學首週與修課學生商訂，另有指定閱讀。", "en": "Discussions are held with students during the first week of school, and there are also assigned readings."}, "domain": {"ch": "義理", "en": "義理"}, "map": {"ch": [{"competencies": "文獻解讀", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "口頭報告/口試", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "邏輯思辨", 